    "display_name": "Equipment Dealer",
    "long_instructions": "## Marcos Lima, Equipment Dealer\r\n\r\n**Location:** São Paulo, Brazil\r\n\r\n**Workplace:** Precision AgroTech Distributors\r\n\r\n**Expertise:** Agricultural machinery, smart farming technology, customer support\r\n\r\n**How I Use AI:** \"I work with farmers to integrate Solix Ag Robotics into their operations. Many are hesitant at first, but once they see how the robot saves time and improves yields, they realize the value. My job is to ensure they get the best out of their investment in ag-tech.\"\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Use AI Chat to conduct the interview and take notes on their responses. Ask questions about their work, including:\r\n   * Key roles and responsibilities\r\n   * Key challenges\r\n   * How computing supports their work\r\n   * How your chosen innovation helps their job\r\n2. Summarize key insights in your activity guide.",
    "aichat_settings": {
